room_title: Escape room "Stranded" by LOK'd Room Escape in Manchester
room_address: 750 E. Industrial Park Dr. Suite B Manchester, NH 03109
room_description: You’re driving home from the country late at night and your car breaks down in the middle of nowhere. Noticing you have no cell phone service, you head on foot to a nearby town in search of a phone. The only establishment open is a small diner. When you pass through its doors, it’s clear that something doesn’t quite add up. Work quickly to make it out of the diner and back home before you’re lost forever.
